-- ONIC Holding to consider Ominvest merger at next board meeting
-- By David French
-- Mon Aug 04, 2014 01:43AM EDT
-- None



DUBAI, Aug 4 (Reuters) - Oman National Investment Corp Holding <ONIC.OM> said on Monday it would discuss a possible merger with Oman International Development and Investment Co <OMAN.OM> (Ominvest) at its next board meeting.

Ominvest said last month it had written to ONIC Holding about forming a strategic arrangement between the two firms, with any tie-up subject to approvals of shareholders and regulators. [ID:nL6N0PV03W] In a short bourse filing on Monday, ONIC Holding said it had received the merger letter and this would be discussed at its next board meeting, after which it would make a further disclosure on the matter.